			<li>Generate makefile with cmake (20%)</li>
			<li>Unit test code with cmake (20%)</li>
			<li>Documentation generated with Doxygen (20%)</li>
			<li>The program can read the input file name from the command line (10%)</li>
			<li>The program can generate csv files correctly (20%)</li>
			<li>Project license (10%)</li>
		</div>
